Muldoonism
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:
Definition:the political (and economic) style of the National Government Prime Minister (Sir) Robert Mulddon (19 - to 1984)
Origin: eponym
Register:
Register 2:
Domain: Politics
Region: [none]
